OL,5, Wealthier households might have to pay 
OL,6, more for the BBC, former chairman      
OL,7, Richard Sharp has suggested.           
OL,9,FThe licence fee system is "regressive",
OL,10,Fhe said, and could instead be replaced 
OL,11,Fby a tax on broadband bills or a       
OL,12,Fhousehold levy based on property value.
OL,14,FThe BBC said the fee was the "agreed   
OL,15,Fmethod of funding until at least 2027" 
OL,16,Fand helped it remain independent.      
OL,18,FMr Sharp resigned as chairman of the   
OL,19,FBBC in April.                          
